
Handling textBoxes and radioButtons:
--- if you have one you can just click on it
--- if you have multiple choices - store the in the list and loop through

Dropdowns:
is menu which give us an opportunity to select one or more options.
type of dropdowns:
1) Single select
2) Multiple select

 Handling dropdown:// how to interact, what kind of approach you use when using dropdown
 1) Click on dropdown and click on the option
 2) using select class.(from selenium library)

 -----in order to use select class we need make sure that we have tag name "select" in the DOM
 -----selecting an option from dropdown can be done in 3 ways:

1- index
1- by visible text
3- by value

-- whenever you interact with multiple elements you store them in the container  such as List, Set...


